    "The amounts can be expressed as a vector, and so can the prices:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\mathbf{q} = \\begin{pmatrix} 2 \\\\ 4 \\\\ 1 \\end{pmatrix} \\quad \\text{(quantities)} \\qquad \\mathbf{p} = \\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ 5 \\\\ 2 \\end{pmatrix} \\quad \\text{(prices)}$$\n",
