    "\n",
    "$$\\begin{pmatrix} 2 & 4 & 1 \\end{pmatrix} \\cdot \\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ 5 \\\\ 2 \\end{pmatrix} = 2 \\cdot 3 + 4 \\cdot 5 + 1 \\cdot 2 = 28$$"
